  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide School Supplies for Social Neglect Victims</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Young people who lived in social neglect, due to lack of care and attention from parents, family or guardians, often face academic backwardness. The project aims to provide youngsters in Casa Alianza with school supplies, uniforms and footwear to continue their formal education in Mexico. The funding will allow us to purchase learning material for the educational program to provide literacy aid to adolescents who have never attended school.</narrative>
  </description>
